md:note.div:
Digtsamling af Ibn Hafāğah al-Andalusī.
Erhvervet af den danske filolog Frederik Christian von Haven (d. 1763) i Kairo 1763. von Haven var deltager i Carsten Niebuhr ekspeditionen 1761-1767.
Cod. Arab. 221

Poetry collection of Ibn Hafāğah al-Andalusī.
Bought 1763 in Cairo by the Danish philologist Frederik Christian von Haven (d. 1763), a member of the Carsten Niebuhr ekspeditionen 1761-1767.
